    ChromocenterAnalysis

    ChromocentersEnhancement
    Several method to create the image of contrasted regions
    Measure2D
    This class allow the determination of two shapes parameter in 2D, Circularity and AspectRatio.
    Measure3D
    Class NucleusMeasure : allow the compute of severals 3Dparameters (shape, lenght) in binary object
    NucleusAnalysis
    Several method to realise and create the outfile for the nuclear Analysis

    NucleusSegmentation
    this class allows the realization of segmention method in the image in input.
    RadialDistance
    this class allows the determination of the radial distance of chromocenters, using the binary nucleus and the image of segmented chromocenters.
